      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Subroutine di editing e arrotondamento importo            *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input  : w-stp-edt-val-val   Valore da arrotondare        *
      *                                                                *
      *    * Output : w-stp-edt-val-edt   Valore editato               *
      *    *          w-stp-edt-val-arr   Valore arrotondato           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       stp-edt-val-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazioni preliminari                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-stp-edt-val-edt      .
           move      zero                 to   w-stp-edt-val-arr      .
       stp-edt-val-100.
